    Scope and Contents
Scalzo recalls her interest and involvement with the arts: attending Kandinsky Academy and the Chicago Art Institute, establishment of the Springfield Art Association, teaching art, collections and exhibits, and types and styles of art. She also discusses studying music at Ursuline Academy in Springfield. 5 tapes, 260 mins. 
Interview by Rhonda Golden, 1983 
